net.dean.jraw.paginators

Class SubmissionSearchPaginator

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dean.jraw.paginators.Paginator<Submission>
      • net.dean.jraw.paginators.SubmissionSearchPaginator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Listing<Submission>>, RedditIterable<Submission>

    public class SubmissionSearchPaginator
extends Paginator<Submission>
    This class allows access to Reddit's search functionality. This class uses a special enum for sorting the values retrieved called SubmissionSearchPaginator.SearchSort. To set this new sorting, use setSearchSorting(SearchSort).
